@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dixvyg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs(v0)
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.32 / tmp + 0.19)) / wp.cos((v0 + 0.17 / tmp + 0.50)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.11)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.29 - v0 + 0.22)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
